 local tangential motions\nmay appear as a consequence of localized substructure, providing a possible\ninterpretation to the \\beta<0 values suggested in observations of M87.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 19:18:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 18:52:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
