\\begin{equation*} (aq;q)_{\\infty}\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{n a^n\nq^{n}}{(q;q)_n} = \\sum_{r=1}^{m}(aq^{r};q^m)_{\\infty}\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}\n\\frac{na^n q^{n r}}{(q^m;q^m)_n}. \\end{equation*} Applications to the Fine\nfunction $F(a,b;t)$ are also considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 21:45:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-01"}
