s MNIST and\nCIFAR-10. By using our method of prediction, and an algorithm implemented by us\nfor a probabilistic exploration of the hyper-parameter space, we were able to\nfind the hyper-parameter settings corresponding to the optimal accuracies\nalready known in literature, at a quite low-cost.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Jun 2019 14:38:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-02"}
